Entry.JapaneseText: キュリア先生って美人だネ。
なるほど…… <Mao>はああいう女性が好みか……
Entry.EnglishText: I see... So that's the type of woman you're interested in...

Entry.JapaneseText: え？ 好みって……いやだなァ、<Eugene>、 そんなんじゃないって……！
Entry.EnglishText: Huh...? My type...? No, <Eugene>, that's not what I meant...!

Entry.JapaneseText: そうだな……まだ<Mao>には早いな。
Entry.EnglishText: I guess you're right... You're too young for that...

Entry.JapaneseText: もーッ!! 子供扱いしないでよねッ！
Entry.EnglishText: Hey! Stop treating me like a kid!
